ai-patthana22.3:0.2_0: under the influence of the Dhamma: the Protector of the Three Worlds
ai-patthana22.3:0.3_0: She’s skilled in moderations and associated with good results.
ai-patthana22.3:1.1_0: Not skilled in the Teaching, or causes and reasons to be associated with cause or condition.
